- System should be able to register dentists
- System should be able to register patients
- Dentists should be able to sign-in 
- Dentist should be able to view listing of their appointments
- System should be able to enroll new Patients
- Patients should be able to call-in to request appointments to see a dentist
- Patients should be able to request appointment by submitting an online form on the ADS website
- System should be able to send a confirmation email notifying the Patient about appointment
- System should provide information about each Surgery
- Patients should be able to sign-in to the system
- Patients should be able to view their appointments, including the information of the dentist who they have been booked
- Patients should be able to cancel or change appointments
